file: CommandRouter.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\CommandRouter"
type: final class
summary: "The CommandRouter class acts as a central dispatcher for ApplyCommand instances, routing them to appropriate handlers based on command kind. It leverages a CommandHandlerRegistry to resolve specific handler implementations and validates command options before routing."
